item.title: new note (near Badacsonyörs, Badacsonytomaj) / * 2020 November 6 18:32 Wild Boar Cottage Created: "A rustic & comfortable 100 year old farm cottage, carefully renovated and decorated, allowing you to relax & unwind in one of the most beautiful parts of Lake Balaton. It is located in the famous wine area of Badacsony and in the immediate vicinity of the Káli-basin, acclaimed for its culinary character. There are many outstanding wineries and restaurants closeby, at the same time the area is most suitable for excursions through fields & forests as well. And the lake is only 5 minutes away !
